pesticides, the agrochemical

00:12:31.550 --> 00:12:33.050 align:middle line:90%
multinationals.

00:12:33.050 --> 00:12:35.420 align:middle line:84%
Amongst the most
widely used products

00:12:35.420 --> 00:12:39.650 align:middle line:84%
in France, the name of one
compound keeps cropping up,

00:12:39.650 --> 00:12:41.570 align:middle line:90%
Folpet.

00:12:41.570 --> 00:12:45.710 align:middle line:84%
It's classified as a likely
carcinogen in the United States

00:12:45.710 --> 00:12:48.770 align:middle line:84%
and as a suspected
carcinogen in Europe.

00:12:48.770 --> 00:12:50.300 align:middle line:90%
It is sold worldwide.

00:12:50.300 --> 00:12:53.600 align:middle line:84%
And there is one multinational
that is way out in front

00:12:53.600 --> 00:12:58.050 align:middle line:84%
when it comes to sales of
products made from Folpet--

00:12:58.050 --> 00:12:59.510 align:middle line:90%
Bayer.

00:12:59.510 --> 00:13:01.430 align:middle line:84%
Bayer-- you've heard
of them, right?

00:13:01.430 --> 00:13:04.370 align:middle line:84%
The chemical giant, the
inventor of aspirin.

00:13:04.370 --> 00:13:07.779 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:13:07.779 --> 00:13:10.710 align:middle line:90%


