closer look, Folpet

00:13:41.960 --> 00:13:45.200 align:middle line:84%
can be found virtually
everywhere in France, even

00:13:45.200 --> 00:13:47.240 align:middle line:90%
in the air that we breathe.

00:13:47.240 --> 00:13:51.080 align:middle line:84%
