for measuring pesticides

00:13:51.080 --> 00:13:55.910 align:middle line:84%
in the air found Folpet in
over 15 of France's 22 regions.

00:13:55.910 --> 00:13:58.400 align:middle line:84%
There is no danger of Bayer
getting a slap on the wrist

00:13:58.400 --> 00:14:00.590 align:middle line:84%
either, as there are
no regulations that

00:14:00.590 --> 00:14:02.740 align:middle line:84%
