00:54:25.260 --> 00:54:27.600 align:middle line:84%
Since this
documentary has begun,

00:54:27.600 --> 00:54:29.700 align:middle line:84%
the pesticide
industry has turned

00:54:29.700 --> 00:54:39.520 align:middle line:90%
over 4,950,000 euros in sales.

00:54:39.520 --> 00:54:45.230 align:middle line:84%
In the great toxic game,
there is no doubt about it--

00:54:45.230 --> 00:54:48.770 align:middle line:84%
the winners and the losers
are always the same.

00:54:48.770 --> 00:54:52.670 align:middle line:90%


